  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK786">
<l>mukanaka naṭpatu naṭpaṉṟu neñcat</l>
<l>takanaka naṭpatē naṭpu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The love that dwells (merely in the smiles of the face is not friendship (but) that which dwells deep in the smiles of the heart is true friendship.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
